snippet.title: Team Sonic Racing - Live Action Trailer
snippet.description:
Team Sonic Racing is out now! In this live-action spot for the game, one supermarket is about to heat up as shopping carts crash and the race to get the last box of Golden O's begins! 

Special thanks to Narthan Barnatt and Jirard The Completionist for joining us for special cameos in this piece!

Available Now - https://www.sonicthehedgehog.com/teamsonicracing
